{"tid":2391583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[恭喜] 支那［吃播］ 腦溢血猝死","createTime":"2021-02-02T10:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T11:27:27.000Z","uid":374134,"like":377,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"edc483b395a44959f3d51e2733dcce75fc0d8996","tid":2391583,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T10:05:48.000Z","msg":"年僅19歲的「吃播」網紅孫藝軒，<span class=\"red\">日前突然腦溢血猝死</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fVGFiux.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfVGFiux.png&h=67263e23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"gold\">有指他為了增加個人知名度，經常暴飲暴食，長期攝取高熱量，高油脂的食物</span>。內媒報道，孫藝軒在社交平台上擁有近50萬粉絲 因風格浮誇，搞笑，備受網民喜愛。他經常與網民分享自己的日常飲食，<span class=\"green\">每頓飯吃3種主食是其影片內容的主要賣點，並曾經憑藉吃反季節水果和四菜一湯收穫大批粉絲。</span>孫藝軒在去世的前幾天曾發布影片但他的黑眼圈明顯，眼袋大，似乎疲勞過度。曾與他合作的網紅紛紛發文悼念，其朋友亦兩人合照，表示對好友死訊不敢相信。藝軒是內地本月第3名突然離世的知名網紅。電視劇《巴啦啦小魔仙》凌美琪的扮演者孫僑潞，本月2日疑因突發心梗猝死，年僅25歲;時尚博主「雅魯藏布江女人」本月5日在飛機上因心臟驟停去世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">Source : XG01 IG</span>"},{"pid":"d3cf8268b8fba57c424900c122e707e0f42dab62","tid":2391583,"uid":8308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T10:06:55.000Z","msg":"RAP"},{"pid":"4bbd33740f76089cf99681f8fbb31c7f42e8b1d0","tid":2391583,"uid":85659,"like":82,"dislike":3,"score":79,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T10:07:18.000Z","msg":"查實睇佢食戈d人算唔算係虐待狂?<br />\n凌遲處死現代版?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b92de27c276dee907f0e3f06749b2a54e6cf5c1","tid":2391583,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T10:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass